# -------------------------------------------------------------
# OnRangeSplit2 - A range split should not lose locks on the LHS of
# the split.
#
# Setup: txn1 acquires lock k1
#        txn2 acquires lock k3
#
# Test:  txn3 enters lock k1s wait-queue
#        txn4 enters lock k3s wait-queue
